{"about_the_game":"<i>&quot;The first casualty of war is innocence&quot;</i><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1905980/extras/Gif0.gif?t=1732133114\" /><br><br>War breeds heroes you've never heard of. You are the ordinary person holding a huge burden of protecting what's most precious and innocent. Fight with hunger, wounds, cold, disease, and enemy cruelty. Defend your family and survive the war!<br><br>Imagine waking up in the middle of the snowy night to the sounds of a falling sky. Explosions, fire, chaos, the frightened whimper of your child. It\u2019s your turn: now or never, slip away from your enemies before it's too late\u2026<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1905980/extras/Gif1.gif?t=1732133114\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>FEW OF MAIN FEATURES IN THE GAME</strong></h2><br>\ud83d\udd4a\ufe0f Building - animal homestead, baby cradle, trough, and more<br>\ud83d\udd4a\ufe0f Crafting - create something useful out of junk<br>\ud83d\udd4a\ufe0f Cooking - prepare all kinds of food out of what you can find<br>\ud83d\udd4a\ufe0f Sneaking - move quietly then you'll survive<br>\ud83d\udd4a\ufe0f Hunting - use guns and provide needed food<br>\ud83d\udd4a\ufe0f Exploring - strange sounds, enemies, unknown territories<br>\ud83d\udd4a\ufe0f Taking care of family - making family safe, fed, and warm<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>PROTECT YOUR FAMILY</strong></h2>As a father, since the first breath of your child, you\u2019ve always known the responsibility relies on your shoulders\u2026 but the stakes were never that high. Do what you must to keep your wife and son alive.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1905980/extras/Gif2.gif?t=1732133114\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>FARM, HUNT, IMPROVISE</strong></h2>Nothing can be taken for granted now. You will have to earn every meal and bargain for each piece of comfort for you and your family using extreme measures. Hunt for wild animals, make forest recipes, and, as a farmer, use your skills to create a new home during the occupation\u2026<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1905980/extras/Gif3.gif?t=1732133114\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>SURVIVE</strong></h2>Sneak, wait for your moment, and ATTACK! Every. Second. Counts. Your enemies are cunning and trained. Can you handle that while being &quot;just&quot; a farmer? Your everyday abilities may come in handy so don\u2019t underestimate yourself and keep trying!<br><br><strong>After all, you\u2019ve got nothing to lose and everything to gain.</strong>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1905980/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1732133114","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1905980/page.bg.jpg?t=1732133114","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1905980/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1732133114","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1905980/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1732133114","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"demos":[{"appid":2105540,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<i>&quot;The first casualty of war is innocence&quot;</i><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1905980/extras/Gif0.gif?t=1732133114\" /><br><br>War breeds heroes you've never heard of. You are the ordinary person holding a huge burden of protecting what's most precious and innocent. Fight with hunger, wounds, cold, disease, and enemy cruelty. Defend your family and survive the war!<br><br>Imagine waking up in the middle of the snowy night to the sounds of a falling sky. Explosions, fire, chaos, the frightened whimper of your child. It\u2019s your turn: now or never, slip away from your enemies before it's too late\u2026<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1905980/extras/Gif1.gif?t=1732133114\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>FEW OF MAIN FEATURES IN THE GAME</strong></h2><br>\ud83d\udd4a\ufe0f Building - animal homestead, baby cradle, trough, and more<br>\ud83d\udd4a\ufe0f Crafting - create something useful out of junk<br>\ud83d\udd4a\ufe0f Cooking - prepare all kinds of food out of what you can find<br>\ud83d\udd4a\ufe0f Sneaking - move quietly then you'll survive<br>\ud83d\udd4a\ufe0f Hunting - use guns and provide needed food<br>\ud83d\udd4a\ufe0f Exploring - strange sounds, enemies, unknown territories<br>\ud83d\udd4a\ufe0f Taking care of family - making family safe, fed, and warm<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>PROTECT YOUR FAMILY</strong></h2>As a father, since the first breath of your child, you\u2019ve always known the responsibility relies on your shoulders\u2026 but the stakes were never that high. Do what you must to keep your wife and son alive.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1905980/extras/Gif2.gif?t=1732133114\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>FARM, HUNT, IMPROVISE</strong></h2>Nothing can be taken for granted now. You will have to earn every meal and bargain for each piece of comfort for you and your family using extreme measures. Hunt for wild animals, make forest recipes, and, as a farmer, use your skills to create a new home during the occupation\u2026<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1905980/extras/Gif3.gif?t=1732133114\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>SURVIVE</strong></h2>Sneak, wait for your moment, and ATTACK! Every. Second. Counts. Your enemies are cunning and trained. Can you handle that while being &q